+
+```bash
+git add src/components/chart/CurveScaleOverlay.tsx src/components/chart/WaterfallChart.tsx
+git commit -m "feat: rewrite CurveScaleOverlay for split/merge modes, wheel-only scaling, shift+drag pan"
